    "body" : "<p>Use the <a href=\"http://maven.apache.org/pom.html#Resources\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><code>&lt;resources&gt;</code> element</a>; nutshell:</p>\n<pre class=\"lang-xml prettyprint-override\"><code>&lt;build&gt;\n&lt;...&gt;\n&lt;resources&gt;\n &lt;resource&gt;\n    &lt;directory&gt;${basedir}/src/main/resources&lt;/directory&gt;\n &lt;/resource&gt;\n\n &lt;resource&gt;\n    &lt;directory&gt;${basedir}/src/main/java&lt;/directory&gt;\n &lt;/resource&gt;\n&lt;/resources&gt;\n&lt;...&gt;\n&lt;/build&gt;\n</code></pre>\n<p><em>Edit:</em> Oh, I thought you meant you wanted a single jar with both normal jar contents and the source.</p>\n"
